data.description: Updated 2 bedroom 1 bath home situated on a little over a half acre in the county with no restrictions.  Home and yard is completely fenced in and includes out buildings for your storage and/or animal needs. The property had a new bathtub installed 2023, new roof 2021, new interior doors, new water heater 2022, HVAC was installed in 2009 and has been regularly serviced by Hiller since 2020, and additional insulation has been added in bedrooms, living room, and under the house between the floor joists.
